{"tid":317970,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"最後通牒，engine一定簡ust","createTime":"2017-07-11T21:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T01:56:01.000Z","uid":31374,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e65ba514ebea66b4f5feae8f28102e05e48e03e8","tid":317970,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T21:47:43.000Z","msg":"係學業前境方面<br />\n科大工程係科大最大學院<br />\n學生人數佔四成<br />\n大量資源都係投放著係SENG度<br />\n而科大工程係全球排第15，絕對唔輸比外國名校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科大遠離市區位於山上<br />\n入面設備先進，師資優良，career support又做到足<br />\n係專心讀書搵好工既好地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以ust亦孕育左唔少頂尖工程師<br />\n科大工程亦有佢獨有既admission scholarship，考得夠好係可以免所有學費額外附加獎學金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係ulife方面<br />\n男既唔洗怕無女，business school女多男少，d囡囡又pure又true，唔會睇唔起N展仔，所以SBM有科大女兒國之稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女既更加唔洗怕無仔，engine男多女少，豬排都變娘娘相信大家都略有所聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且ust yr1 必定有hall住，可以體驗一下社堂生活，充實非常。<br />\n校方亦都驚大家太熱愛讀書，忘記左做運動，第一年係要大家完成HLTH1010呢個course，比大家體驗唔同類型既運動，強身健體又陪養興趣。想變得更強既亦都可以玩rowing/科大龍，挑戰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIn just engine,we trust!"},{"pid":"5c220b4dbce89133ac3db4f4143dc21d2cbc0c39","tid":317970,"uid":31374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T21:49:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔記得左<br />\n祝大家齊齊入科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"76c4abce73f26eae78122df54b310a1c88c49a20","tid":317970,"uid":113465,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T22:07:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗怕冇女，因為一定冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b228a552797d24e104d7e181d779d3495cf665","tid":317970,"uid":1342,"like":0,"dislike":0